items.title: Bossa Nova Beach Cafe Ambience with Relaxing Latin Coffee Shop Music, Ocean Waves, & Soft Chatter
items.description:
Enjoy this Bossa Nova Beach Cafe Ambience with relaxing latin coffee shop music, ocean waves, and soft background chatter. Listen to the the easy going bossa nova jazz music while you take in the view of the tropical ocean waves rolling onto the beach in Rio De Janeiro, Brazil. Let these soothing sounds of a latin cafe / seaside cafe and smooth jazz lounge music create an atmosphere of peace and calm around you as you work, sleep, study, mediate, or simply relax.
This 8-hour calming bossa nova music and waves ambience video was created by blending many layers of relaxing ambient sounds together to create an original background soundscape meant to help reduce stress and anxiety. Many people find ambient videos like this helpful for working, reading, sleeping, or general relaxation. All sounds and images were created by Calmed By Nature or used with permission.
